{"tid":2403643,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"中原大灣區指數報121.05創歷史新高 分析：新年前偷步小陽春","createTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T09:08:02.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"561dfe4102938cc153bffd0fe557e227f6c4048e","tid":2403643,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"中原大灣區指數報121.05創歷史新高 分析：新年前偷步小陽春<br />\n14:45 2021/02/11<br />\n<br />\n&quot;2021年1月中原大灣區指數突破121點，創歷史新高，報121.05，較上月升0.55%。12個指數中共11個指數錄得上升，幅度由0.17%至4.4%不等，唯獨香港指數錄得跌幅。1月份共6個指數創歷史新高，除大灣區指數外，廣州、深圳、東莞、佛山及中山指數亦於1月份創出歷史新高，深圳指數連續17個月創新高......<br />\n<br />\n......陳永傑指，香港於農曆新年前，亦一如其它大灣區城市，出現農曆新年前的小陽春，今年因疫情封關，香港市民留港度歲，料小陽春將延續至新年後整個二月份。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2877352/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%A0%B1121.05%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%20%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%81%B7%E6%AD%A5%E5%B0%8F%E9%99%BD%E6%98%A5?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2877352%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A0%25B1121.05%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2520%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2598%25A5%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=c1d6504f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2877352/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%A0%B1121.05%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%20%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%81%B7%E6%AD%A5%E5%B0%8F%E9%99%BD%E6%98%A5?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">通關後香港樓價將再進一步飆升，所以想上車就要快!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ae6d95997b34ae055137ea6eb5f7a7551213f417","tid":2403643,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"我未買，要追貨"}]}